 further confusion in the case, the DCP told the media she was going towards Dumduma from Master Canteen when she was molested in the auto. \"It is being investigated as to why she was going to Dumduma late at night. A manhunt has been launched to nab the culprits,\" Singh said. A case has been registered at Khandagiri police station and investigation is on, he said and denied the girl was raped.Though the victim did not suggest direct complicity of the auto driver in the case, police said they would bring the driver under the purview of investigation too. \"We have detained an auto driver suspecting his involvement in the case,\" Singh said. Asked whether the girl knew the driver and co-passengers, Singh said, \"She gave us a statement that she did not know them before. She also did not read the name of the driver from his identity card, pasted behind the driver's seat.\"", "source": "toi", "date": "2012-12-25"}
