y alert police and rush to the spot,\" the inspector said. The application can be downloaded from . Similar free applications are also available at www.neverwalkalone.com, ,As a precautionary measure, the Madhapur police have gathered details of 2000 auto drivers plying vehicles from various stands near Hi-Tec City. All these autos were given unique easily recognizable number, which is displayed on the vehicle. Women employees were also asked to SMS the number to their family members or friends as soon as they get into the vehicle as a precautionary measure.", "source": "toi", "date": "2012-12-25"}
