s, they end up doing various stunts which also leads to disaster,\" said Dr Sanjay Kumawat, from Bombay Psychiatrists Society. \"Parents need to strictly discourage children from indulging in such activities before they are lawfully entitled to do so,\" added Kumawat.", "source": "toi", "date": "2012-12-25"}
