006. Koli confessed to killing several victims, including the minor girl, and discarding their body parts and belongings in the backyard and inside the drain near the house.On February 13, 2009, the duo was sentenced to death in the first verdict in the Nithari killings. However, Pandher was acquitted by the Allahabad high court on September 11, 2011. On May 12, 2010, Koli was sentenced to death for the second time. On September 27, 2010, he was sentenced for the rape and murder of another nine-year-old. The fourth sentence came on December 21, 2010 for the murder of a 12-year-old girl.", "source": "toi", "date": "2012-12-25"}
